c: 17
v: 60
t: "Era jjukira bwe twakugamba nti mazima Mukama omulabiriziwo yeetoolodde abantu (abo, n'olwekyo tobatya) era tetwaleeta ndooto eyo gye twakulaga okugyako olw'okugezesa abantu era mu ngeri y'emu omuti ogwakolimirwa mu Kur’ani nakyo kigezo era tubatiisa (nga tubabuulira) ebiribaawo ku lunaku lw'enkomerero naye tebibongera okugyako okubula okuyitirivu"